Primitive level viewer for Metro 2033
=====================================

Install
-------

Install perl if needed ( strawberryperl.com for windows is good ).
From command line run CPAN installation tool:

$ cpan
cpan shell -- CPAN exploration and modules installation (v1.9800)
Enter 'h' for help.
cpan>


from there, install prerequisite modules by typing:

install Moose
install Prima
install OpenGL
install Prima::OpenGL

Unpack level data
-----------------

m2033unp.exe content.vfs0 c:\m2033data

Run the viewer
--------------

perl level-view.pl c:\m2033data\content\maps\l05_lost_tunnel

Enjoy!

Dmitry Karasik <dmitry@karasik.eu.org>
